msgid "IPS mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/ips.rst:84
msgid ""
"When enabled, the system can drop suspicious packets. In order for this "
"to work, your network card needs to support netmap. The action for a rule"
" needs to be \"drop\" in order to discard the packet, this can be "
"configured per rule or ruleset (using an input filter)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/ips.rst:88
msgid "Promiscuous mode"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/ips.rst:88
msgid ""
"Listen to traffic in promiscuous mode. (all packets in stead of only the "
"ones addressed to this network interface)"
msgstr ""

